            </font><font color="#ff0000">Stock Photos</font></b>

            </font>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">From: <a href="mailto:RMaxim@casedesign.com">Rachel
            Maxim</a></font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2"><i>Can anyone recommend a good source
            for the "generic" photos of individuals or groups of
            people that appear on many website home pages?</i></font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">Having searched hundreds of stock
            photography sites, I always come back to <a href="http://www.gettyimages.com">www.gettyimages.com</a>.&nbsp;
            Other good sites I'd recommend are <a href="http://www.corbisimages.com">www.corbisimages.com</a>,&nbsp;
            <a href="http://www.comstock.com">www.comstock.com</a> , and <a href="http://www.picturequest.com">www.picturequest.com</a>&nbsp;
            which searches many of the larger popular sites.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">Rachel Maxim&nbsp;<br>
